        "text_mziyCR": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As a world-leading developer in pH and titration science, we help professionals and enthusiasts meet their daily testing needs across a wide range of applications. We provide easy-to-use, well-adapted instruments at competitive prices, supported by fast and reliable customer service.</p><p>Our philosophy of staying as close to our customers as possible has resulted in dedicated sales and technical support offices in more than 40 countries. Our ambition to be an innovator has led to many world-first developments in testing instruments, and we continue to innovate and introduce new solutions to the market in direct response to our customers’ needs.</p><p>You will find Hanna instruments used in almost every imaginable application — from hobbyists caring for their home aquariums, to food artisans, and all the way to national and international brands across all industrial sectors. Hanna is a trusted name with over 3,000 products, all manufactured in our ISO 9001-certified European production facility.</p>",
